{"type":null,"faqId":49850,"title":"彩信发送/接收失败的可能原因，解决方法","answer":"<div id=\"body43762514\">\n<p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__p21513262\">\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__p38076008173329\">彩信发送、接收失败，原因可能有以下几种：</p>\n<ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__ul1485706617341\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li322925617341\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">网络状态或信号不好。请稍后重试发送。</li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li8813537173416\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">收件人号码信息填写不正确。请更正后重发彩信。</li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li44569763173437\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">编辑的彩信超过了300KB，不能发送。请删除一些彩信内容，再尝试发送。</li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li5114387717353\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">欠费。请缴费后重新发送。</li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li56032770173537\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">手机内存不足。请释放一部分内存，使剩余空间大于300K。</li>\n</ul>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__p28371053\">如果上述原因都不是，请采取下面解决方法：</p>\n<ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__ul46537419174035\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li54664915174035\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">彩信发送失败：</li>\n</ul>\n<ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__ol65432194173828\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li54505725173828\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>首先，请检查手机APN设置，确认手机已有正确的彩信APN；</span></li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li20789477173828\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>如果APN码正确，请您关掉WIFI查看是否可以正常发送；</span></li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li52887571173828\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>如果仍不能正常发送，请您将SIM卡放到其他品牌手机上，查看是否可以正常发送彩信；</span></li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li6226095173828\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>如果仍不能正常发送，请您备份数据，恢复出厂设置尝试；</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__p65272892174142\">如果上述方法仍未解决问题，请您携带购机凭证到附近网点检测。</p>\n<ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__ul2203690817420\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li4881899317420\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">彩信接收失败：</li>\n</ul>\n<ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__ol4175628817426\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li5548227617426\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>首先，请检查手机是否开通数据业务；</span></li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li9301581174211\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>如果已经开通，请您关闭wifi功能尝试;</span></li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__li27273437174214\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><span>如果仍不能正常发送，请您将SIM卡放到其他同类品牌手机中，查看是否可以接收彩信；</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264323__p52187591174142\">如果上述方法仍未解决问题，请您联系运营商解决。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"familylinks\"></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264323","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615544000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"彩信,短息,发送,接收,失败","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}